{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2510982, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "光着最干净", "timestamp": 1631675599, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2510986, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我也觉得地面不干净，所以一般都飞在空中", "timestamp": 1631675649, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2510995, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "泻药 人在霍格沃兹，刚下扫帚", "timestamp": 1631675741, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511003, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有个洁癖朋友这样说，洞主觉得有点道理，不想变成洁癖啊，请字母君们说服洞主", "timestamp": 1631675822, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511018, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本来喜欢游泳跳舞瑜伽现在都觉得脏了呜呜呜", "timestamp": 1631675985, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511021, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我每天都有在碰裙子、裤子、鞋、椅子、地面，但是从未因此感染病菌，因此我认为它们已经足够干净了", "timestamp": 1631676050, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511037, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": 2511021, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 那你应该感谢你体内的免疫系统", "timestamp": 1631676227, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511049, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": 2511037, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 谢谢，很有道理，不过就是觉得膈应，像是上完卫生间不洗手一样", "timestamp": 1631676360, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511050, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": 2511021, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 这么说不准确，但总之目前为止我没有察觉到自己因此受到什么损害", "timestamp": 1631676362, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511094, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "再换个角度想，裙子、裤子、鞋、椅子会接触的物体，我裸露的肌肤也会接触，两者不干净的程度相当，尤其是不干净的下限是相当的，所以触碰这些物体一般不会使我裸露的肌肤不干净程度变大，并且不会让我裸露的肌肤不干净的程度突破我所认识到它不干净程度的底线......\n至于地面，我会想，它的灰尘源自大气沉降，而我本来就生活在大气中，只是地面上的灰尘浓度变大了...", "timestamp": 1631676735, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511124, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 基本被你说服了！但还是接受不了地面，鞋到处踩，会踩很脏的地面比如卫生间，太难以接受", "timestamp": 1631677031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511149, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大部分地方都比你很久没洗的手干净 ", "timestamp": 1631677222, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511155, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": 2511124, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 鞋踩的时候脏的粒子会分散到各处，每天人走这么多步，脏的浓度也被分散了", "timestamp": 1631677277, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511428, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz寝室里同时穿三套睡衣：洗澡穿的，洗完了坐在座位上玩儿穿的，睡觉穿的，彼此之间互不接触。或许可以参考", "timestamp": 1631679444, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511809, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz家里就是洁癖很严重，从外面回到家会立即洗手换衣服，外面穿过的衣服裤子绝对不接触家里的椅子、床etc，夏天穿短袖还会洗手臂", "timestamp": 1631682661, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2511824, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 479418, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就是说洁癖有洁癖的生活方式，cz在宿舍也基本遵循这些规则，心里舒服而且也没有太麻烦", "timestamp": 1631682759, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 479418, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "会有人觉得裙子、裤子、鞋、椅子、地面不干净所以尽量不碰吗？", "timestamp": 1631675489, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631682759, "url": "", "vote": {}}}